text: Dorfer is the surname of the following people: * Alfred Dorfer (b. 1961), Austrian comedian, writer and actor * Bruno Dorfer, deserter of the German Kriegsmarine during World War II * Franz Dorfer (1950–2012), Austrian boxer ==See also== * Kristina Dörfer (b. 1984), German singer and television actress * Fabian Dörfler (b. 1983), German slalom canoer
title: Dorfer
